Nitin Varma, the producer and 
director of the Tennis Channel's "Signature Series on Bud 
Collins," discusses the life and times of Collins, an American  
journalist and television sportscaster who is best known for his
tennis coverage. Collins, a member of both the International 
Tennis Hall of Fame and the Sportswriters Hall of Fame, is 
currently a commentator for the Tennis Channel's Grand Slam 
tournaments.   Varma speaks with Bloomberg's  Kathleen Hays  on 
Bloomberg Radio's "The Hays Advantage."   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 07:07
 